         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e16320"> </a>Remove the engine from the frame (<a href="44894.html#DUCc6004ac024f010058895df5a40d4efd2">Removing the engine</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e16325"> </a>Remove the timing parts (<a href="45036.html#DUC5af7ddf82516100581d2e6ffb59083d2">Removing the timing outer covers</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e16330"> </a>Remove the camshafts (<a href="45072.html#DUC92cac200251a100584bad8c3784850d2">Removing the camshafts</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e16335"> </a>Remove the complete cylinder head unit (<a href="45087.html#DUCbfdc2068251a100584bcd8c3784850d2">Removing the engine heads</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e16340"> </a>Remove the cylinder/piston assembly (<a href="45114.html#DUCad1f8410256a10058d3dd14d9928c7d2">Removing the cylinder/piston assembly</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e16345"> </a>Remove the generator side cover and the generator (<a href="45174.html#DUCf616ff28259110058912eb60359b4bd2">Removing the generator cover</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e16350"> </a>Remove the starter motor (<a href="45211.html#DUCc66422f826841005887be38e40fd97d2">Removing the starter motor</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e16355"> </a>Remove the clutch cover (<a href="45136.html#DUC2ab31d18257c10058cb5f04d994144d2">Removing the clutch cover</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e16360"> </a>Remove the clutch unit (<a href="45124.html#DUCe33f2810257a10058caaf04d994144d2">Removing the clutch</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e16365"> </a>Remove the oil pump (<a href="44898.html#DUC1994777824f2100583a2b051d7198fd2">Removing the oil pump</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e16370"> </a>Remove the primary drive gear (<a href="45144.html#DUC41e9ea28257e100580b68e32a097eed2">Removing the primary drive gear</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e16376"> </a>Remove the mesh filter (<a href="77245.html#DUCc57ed0d029f510058c2bed44952c77d2">Changing engine oil and filter cartridge</a>)
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e16382"> </a>Loosen screw (1) and remove the oil breather valve (2) from the engine with O-rings (3). Check the condition of O-rings&nbsp;(3)
            and renew them if necessary.
         </div>
